\norm{u_{i}-w} & \xrightarrow{i\to\infty}d=\inf_{u\in K}\norm{u-w}\\
\norm{u_{j}-w} & \xrightarrow{j\to\infty}d=\inf_{u\in K}\norm{u-w}
