Maximize 
\begin_inset Formula $\abs{S\left(u\right)}$
\end_inset

 on 
\begin_inset Formula $\left\{ u\in H\big|\norm u=1\right\} $
\end_inset

:
\begin_inset Newline newline
\end_inset

Choose a maximizing sequence 
\begin_inset Formula $\left(u_{n}\right)$
\end_inset

