\end_inset

.
 Now we write
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
\Omega & =\bigcup_{N}K_{N}
\end{align*}

\end_inset

with 
\begin_inset Formula $K_{N}\subseteq K_{N+1}$
\end_inset

